headline: Axiado and Inventec Showcase AI-Driven Platform Security and Autonomous System Management for NVIDIA Blackwell and Intel MGX Servers at OCP Global Summit 2025
summary: OCP Global Summit 2025 — Axiado Corporation, a leading AI-driven, hardware-anchored platform security and system management solutions company, today announced a collaboration with Inventec, a global innovator in server and storage solutions. At the OCP Global Summit, the companies will demonstrate how Axiado's Trusted Control/Compute Unit (TCU) powers Inventec's NVIDIA Blackwell GB200-based servers and Intel-based MGX 4U CX8 platforms with silicon-anchored trust and autonomous AI intelligence.
